Release Notes:
Egypt: Old Kingdom - Master of History might be the most unusual DLC
you have ever discovered. We heed the communitys critique and
reinvented the game anew, presenting the opportunity to forego every
possible constraint. Play away and develop your state and technologies
endlessly. Turn off the trials and events. Add more enemies - Sea
peoples, mummies, and even aliens! Create the history, as you wish,
according to your own tastes. Its your history and you are the Master!
Endless Game
No more restraints! With the endless mode you can continue the game
after the 300 turn and to test your talents battling new enemies. Will
you be able to get to turn 400?
Customizable micromanagement
Do you like to build and develop a city? Or would you rather focus on
the global events? Its all in your hands - adjust the amount of
micromanagement and play the game the way you like it!
Crazy Egypt
No, its not Halloween yet - we simply added a few absolutely crazy
modes. Will you be able to defeat zombie-mummies or free Egypt from
the alien yoke? Youll never know until you try!
RIPPED: Nothing

4. Enjoy!
Remember to support quality games!
